## Project Overview

This is a Next.js 16 starter kit with:
- **Framework**: Next.js 16.1.1 (App Router), React 19
- **Language**: TypeScript 5 (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 (OKLCH color system), CSS Variables
- **UI**: shadcn/ui (New York style), Radix UI primitives
- **Icons**: lucide-react
- **Theme**: next-themes (dark/light mode)

